    "body" : "<p>you can do </p>\n\n<pre><code>findViewById\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>from the radio group .</p>\n\n<p>Here it is sample :</p>\n\n<pre><code>((RadioButton)my_radio_group.findViewById(R.id.radiobtn_veg)).setChecked(true);\n</code></pre>\n"
