    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1583570536,
    "creation_date" : 1583570536,
    "answer_id" : 60575816,
    "question_id" : 6440259,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Here is a <strong>Kotlin</strong> extension to get the <strong>correct position even if</strong> your group contains a TextView or any non-RadioButton.</p>\n\n<pre><code>fun RadioGroup.getCheckedRadioButtonPosition(): Int {\n    val radioButtonId = checkedRadioButtonId\n    return children.filter { it is RadioButton }\n        .mapIndexed { index: Int, view: View -&gt;\n            index to view\n        }.firstOrNull {\n            it.second.id == radioButtonId\n        }?.first ?: -1\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 6657042,
      "reputation" : 1201,
      "user_id" : 9150584,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/mxr5j.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Meysam Keshvari",
